and of trying to start a war with Pakistan to deflect attention.</s>

<s docid="AP900718-0069" num="12" wdcount="28"> Relations between Pakistan and
India worsened in January when Indian soldiers cracked down on Moslem
militants in Kashmir who are seeking independence from India or union with
Pakistan.</s>

<s docid="AP900718-0069" num="13" wdcount="11"> At least 792 people have been
killed in Kashmir since then.</s>

<s docid="AP900821-0092" num="18" wdcount="16"> Despite the tension, officials
